34 SUMMARY
3355 This amendment, which is the minority report of the committee, replaces the resolve
3366 and changes the title. It establishes the Working Group on Modernizing State Grants,
3377 Contracts and Procurement to examine the State's grant and public procurement practices
3388 and make recommendations to the Department of Administrative and Financial Services.
3399 The working group is required to submit a report, which may include recommendations for
4400 legislation, by November 4, 2026 to the joint standing committee of the Legislature having
4411 jurisdiction over state and local government matters and the Department of Administrative
